cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on robotic assembly and presents a high-accuracy pose estimation procedure for a specific assembly task. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper uses a depth camera for pose estimation and deep convolutional neural networks for detection and refinement. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses deep learning techniques for pose estimation and network training. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves the use of AI techniques for robotic assembly. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the control of a robotic system for assembly.
